                        <interp inst="t18360201-name-510" type="given" value="GEORGE"></interp>GEORGE HEMINGTON</persName>
                  </hi> (<hi rend="italic">police-constable D</hi> 140.) I took the prisoner into custody, and found I his pocket a duplicate for this bed—he said it was his own.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
