                        <interp inst="t18360201-name-512" type="given" value="THOMAS"></interp>THOMAS BRIDGEN</persName>
                  </hi>. This is my bed—he used to be with me when he was out of place—he use to do part of my work—I have had no quarrel with him—he behaved very well before—he never paid me any money with respect to this bed.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Prisoner. Q.</hi> Did not I give you four sovereign four years ago last June, which you sent down to Old Windsor? <hi rend="italic">A.</hi> No; I never had any money of him, I am sure of that. 
